verbose_text: There was a significant positive relation between nestling total Ig levels and LPS-reactive antibodies at day 6 (beta = 0.44, F 1,111.1 = 29.714, P < 0.001; Year : F 1,31.7 = 44.221, P < 0.001) and day 14 post-hatch (beta = 0.20, F 1,103.8 = 8.898, P = 0.004; Year : F 1,35.26 = 21.036, P < 0.001).
